{"tid":54285,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翁靜晶接死亡恐嚇","createTime":"2016-12-25T11:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T11:59:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4606c988a20602827a744c4b2afa96ad0daa9491","tid":54285,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19876161&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19876161%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161225&d=a0EL2TqwfpJ7CvUbxbS21n8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=a9799bbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19876161%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161225&h=0f895546\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19876161&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161225</a><br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶接死亡恐嚇<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n■翁靜晶（右）早年為定慧寺出錢出力，後揭發假和尚事件而收到恐嚇。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶年前為打擊假和尚不遺餘力，設立「佛門警訊」，又扮「鬼妹」放蛇。昨日有周刊指翁靜晶調查時，疑觸動佛門中人利益，令她收死亡恐嚇。翁靜晶昨日在電話中直認：「調查員同假和尚組織有一啲聯繫，知道佢哋用文字寫咗『幹掉她』，『她』即係翁靜晶，等我入內地時就會落手。」<br />\n<br />\n問翁靜晶可擔心人身安全？她說：「係驚出事冇人知，𠵱家大家都知，如果成功都唔會冇人追究。」翁靜晶直認有過內心掙扎，但為了善心的捐款人要站出來，她說：「如我一放手，咁呢個錢同塊地就冇㗎喇！唔可以落係壞人手中。」而她覺得在香港報警作用不大，至於內地則不便透露。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：嵐山<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;伍姑娘抱敏之囝囝晒母愛<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;打頭陣演出梅姐慈善騷　海俊傑明年3月澳洲娶化妝師"},{"pid":"050580b2f2c76bea6120655e620ca3fc741376ef","tid":54285,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161225/280pix/25ec4p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161225%2F280pix%2F25ec4p7.jpg&h=7bcb585f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ff8967bb466a5ba2010fe1caab9635f8e5190d3","tid":54285,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"超積極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a073bddca5f44208272c744d0f5601896238f898","tid":54285,"uid":19599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLXQsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLXQsu.jpg&h=e7a01d3d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}